# CurveLens ICE Brent cron template — intentionally non-executable.
#
# Brent is experimental. Do not register or enable schedules from this file.
# A future reviewed schedule must use CCVM_PRODUCT=brent, read AGENTS.md plus
# deployments/brent/AGENTS.md, verify both authorized ICE settlement exports,
# and invoke `$curvelens-daily-analysis`. It must resume persisted state,
# default to no delivery, and ship disabled for explicit approval.
